      ** +--------------------------------------+
     D GenOkFlag       S              1    Import
 
      * Header record datastructure
     D HdrRcdIn      E DS                  EXTNAME(FT101HSPD)
 
      * Second DS for access programs, long data structure
     D DSSDY         E DS                  EXTNAME(DSSDY)
 
     D  A1             S              1    DIM(16)
 
     D i               S              3  0
